data.description: One Owner Home with lots to offer! This well maintained home has 2 large living areas or the bonus room could be 4th bedroom as it has a HUGE CLOSET! All bedrooms are nice size.  Main living has beautiful fireplace and built-ins. Fresh Paint in 2 of the 4 bedrooms and 1 of the bathrooms.  Lovely landscaping in front and backyard, backyard is spacious and fully fenced.  Putnam City Schools, conveniently located to everything!
